Que souhaitez vous faire ?
- Prendre des affaires
	- Sac à dos [if PlayerGlobals.getBedroomInfo("closet","backpack") == false][else="disable"]
		do PlayerGlobals.addClosetChoice("backpack")
	- Pullover [if  PlayerGlobals.getBedroomInfo("closet","pullover") == false ][else="disable"]
		do PlayerGlobals.addClosetChoice("pullover")
	- Casque de vélo [if  PlayerGlobals.getBedroomInfo("closet","helmet") == false ][else="disable"]
		do PlayerGlobals.addClosetChoice("helmet")
